L'Esprit Blanc: Restaurants and Hotels by Georges Blanc

   Each of these establishments presents a distinctive feature; it may be
   located on the riverbank, in the heart of a nearby city or in the
   countryside, in Mâcon or Beaujolais regions.

   These places can offer a pleasant and tasty break while you are
   visiting or working in this beautiful region, or on your way to
   Southern France, the Alpes, Switzerland or Italy.

   Over the last 20 years, we tried to create around this concept a
   certain number of establishments that represent the perfect combination
   of our values. This is what we call “L’Esprit Blanc”: Authenticity,
   Simplicity, Quality, Conviviality and Affordability.

Restaurant Le Saint Laurent
in Macon
Since 1992

   On the banks of the Saône, right in front of Mâcon, Le Saint Laurent
   offers a unique view of the Old Saint-Laurent Bridge, a scheduled
   monument dating back to the 11^th century.
   More Book your table Set menus
   facebook instragram tripadvisor
