Brasserie Le Splendid
in Lyon
since 2001

   In front of the old Brotteaux Station, a scheduled monument situated
   just 300 m from Parc de la Tête d’Or, a 2-minute walk from Lyon Part
   Dieu Station and the shopping center, Georges Blanc pays a tribute to
   the famous “Mother Cooks” in this beautiful Brasserie: Le Splendid.
   More Book your table Set menus
   facebook instagram tripadvisor
   < span > michelin dish </ span > Georges Blanc
   Le Spendid Georges Blanc

Restaurant L’Embarcadère
in Jassans Riottier
since 2011

   Half way between Beaujolais, Dombes and Lyonnais mountains, in the
   heart of a 12-acre Park by the Saône river, L’Embarcadère offers a
   country cuisine that is reinterpreted with the seasons.

   More Book your table Set menus
